strings: <voice_0x01000B6C><se_def>awesome!: ...it is perfect! The match was rematched at a bar in Simpson City. be proud of yourself
<voice_0x01000B6D><se_def>China: Word spreads fast. The Templars have a vast network of personal connections...
<voice_0x01000B6E><se_def>awesome!: That's a shame on our monasteries! - Fuck you!
<voice_0x01000B6F><se_def>awesome!: Yes, it is filthy. We would have been through a lot if you had not been born.
<voice_0x01000B72><se_def>awesome!: I worry about the idea of genocide.
<voice_0x01000B74><se_def>awesome!: The principal landlord of the temple demands a fine.
<voice_0x01000B75><se_def>awesome!: I kicked you out of the temple. You won't get out of here. This is nothing! spook
<voice_0x01000B76><se_def>awesome!: If you dare to disturb me, you will be expelled from the organization! Don't believe that the abbot can protect you this time!
